## 3. Secrets / Sensitive Data Scanning

### TruffleHog
```bash
trufflehog git https://github.com/org/repo.git
trufflehog filesystem /path/to/downloaded/repo
```

### Gitleaks
```bash
gitleaks detect --source /path/to/repo -v
gitleaks detect --source . --report-path gitleaks_report.json
```

### git-dumper (recover exposed .git directories)
```bash
git-dumper https://target.com/.git/ output_folder/
```

### LinkFinder (JS file endpoint extraction)
```bash
python3 linkfinder.py -i https://target.com/app.js -o cli
python3 linkfinder.py -i https://target.com -d -o results.html    # crawl + JS extraction
```

### SecretFinder
```bash
python3 SecretFinder.py -i https://target.com/main.js -o cli
```

