## 4. API Testing / Fuzzing

### Kiterunner (API endpoint brute force)
```bash
kr scan https://target.com -w routes-large.kite -o api_results.txt
```

### feroxbuster (recursive content discovery, good for APIs)
```bash
feroxbuster -u https://target.com -w wordlist.txt -x json,xml
```

