## 9. Hash Cracking (heavier / GPU-based)

### Hashcat
```bash
hashcat -m 0 -a 0 hash.txt rockyou.txt              # MD5
hashcat -m 1000 -a 0 hash.txt rockyou.txt           # NTLM
hashcat --show hash.txt
```

---

## 10. Fast Port/Service Scanning (large scope)

### Masscan
```bash
masscan -p1-65535 target.com --rate=1000 -oL masscan_out.txt
```

### RustScan
```bash
rustscan -a target.com -- -sV -sC
```

